{"id":231664396,"title":"Kirk Hinrich 有人還記得他嗎？","content":"剛剛在某籃球粉專看到NBA Live 2004的廣告\n代言的是03梯的幾位新秀\nhttps://youtu.be/eX7txHCE6oM\nMelo跟Bosh就不用多說了，兩個都是全明星等級的好手\n不過那時候還沒戴上護目鏡的Kirk Hinrich，不知道有誰還記得他呢？\nhttps://i.imgur.com/4vsW53Y.png\n\n作為03梯首輪第七順位的樂透秀卻只有新秀第一隊跟年度防守二隊的榮譽，而且連明星賽都沒有參加過，這樣的成績顯然是不及格的\n不過好像也很少人說他是水貨？\n06/07球季場均4.2次三分出手還有四成以上的命中率，生涯三分命中率也是夠水準的.375\n\n生涯最大的污點大概是06年入選了美國參加世錦賽的「惡夢隊」吧xD 輸給希臘之後直接送西班牙一個兵不血刃的金牌(希臘全場只拿下47分是史上最慘https://i.imgur.com/lfBinxB.jpg\n\n有三分有防守有組織，感覺就是稍微弱化的Mike Conley (？\n不知道對他還有印象的版友會怎麼評價這位球員？","excerpt":"剛剛在某籃球粉專看到NBA Live 2004的廣告，代言的是03梯的幾位新秀，Melo跟Bosh就不用多說了，兩個都是全明星等級的好手，不過那時候還沒戴上護目鏡的Kirk Hinrich，不知道有誰還記得他呢？","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"863b960a-72a8-4479-80a2-b976275c002e","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-07-12T08:06:14.714Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-12T08:06:14.714Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":6,"tags":[],"topics":["NBA"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{},"forumName":"籃球","forumAlias":"basketball","school":"卡螺絲啦！","department":"mellamocarlos","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":6}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/4vsW53Y.png"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/lfBinxB.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"f35e584b-78c9-4f5f-871b-a054f5081f56","url":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eX7txHCE6oM/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eX7txHCE6oM/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eX7txHCE6oM/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-07-12T08:06:14.714Z","updatedAt":"2019-07-12T08:06:14.714Z"},{"id":"f35e584b-78c9-4f5f-871b-a054f5081f56","url":"https://youtu.be/eX7txHCE6oM","normalizedUrl":"https://youtu.be/eX7txHCE6oM","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/eX7tx